{"id":"concepts/narcissist-father-as-mirror","title":"Narcissist father as mirror","type":"concepts","html":"<blockquote>\n<p>Stub. The diagnosis Yahir runs on himself — being marked permanently by <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/dad-yahir\">Dad's</a> inheritance is structurally the same as being marked by ink/piercings (per <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2023-04-21-thoughts-about-tattoo\">the tattoo doc</a>). <em>\"I look like my mom / dad looks like his dad / a cycle that has no end\"</em> (<a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2023-05-05-happy-birthday-poem\">2023 05 05 happy birthday poem</a>).</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Connections: <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/dad-yahir\">dad yahir</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/lineage-as-fate\">lineage as fate</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/alcoholism-in-the-family\">alcoholism in the family</a> · body as permanent record · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2024-01-04-thoughts-on-1323-dad-in-bad-state\">2024 01 04 thoughts on 1323 dad in bad state</a></p>\n","related":[{"id":"concepts/alcoholism-in-the-family","label":"Alcoholism in the family"},{"id":"unresolved/body-as-permanent-record","label":"body as permanent record"},{"id":"entities/dad-yahir","label":"Dad Yahir"},{"id":"summaries/2023-05-05-happy-birthday-poem","label":"Happy birthday poem (Feb 7th — Yahir & Dad)"},{"id":"summaries/2024-01-04-thoughts-on-1323-dad-in-bad-state","label":"Jan 2024 thoughts — dad in worst state, Vic dead, Emilio as anchor (the late-night-cry note)"},{"id":"concepts/lineage-as-fate","label":"Lineage as Fate"},{"id":"entities/maya","label":"Maya"},{"id":"summaries/2023-04-21-thoughts-about-tattoo","label":"Thoughts about tattoo (4/21/23 fragment)"}]}
